n in Wales and Scotland, having been borne by the patron saint of Wales (  see  Dewi   ) and by two medieval kings of Scotland."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"When Sir David Lochore was born in 1210, in Lochore, Fife, Scotland, his father, Sir Duncan Lochore, was 14 and his mother, Mrs Lochore, was 15. He had at least 1 daughter with Margaret Heiress. He died in 1290, in Lochore, Fife, Scotland, United Kingdom, at the age of 80."},"et":{"1210–1290":"1210–1290","1210–Female":"1210–Surnud","1240–1325":"1240–1325","1196–1290":"1196–1290","1196–1235":"1196–1235","1325":"1325","1235":"1235","1210":"1210","before 1210":"enne 1210","about 1235":"umbes 1235","1240":"1240","1196":"1196","1290":"1290","Lochore, Fife, Scotland":"Lochore, Fife, Scotland","Scotland":"Scotland","Fife, Scotland":"Fife, Scotland","Lochore, Fife, Scotland, United Kingdom":"Lochore, Fife, Šotimaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1210–1290":"1210–1290","1210–Female":"1210–Kuollut","1240–1325":"1240–1325","1196–1290":"1196–1290","1196–1235":"1196–1235","1325":"1325","1235":"1235","1210":"1210","before 1210":"ennen vuotta 1210","about 1235":"noin 1235","1240":"1240","1196":"1196","1290":"1290","Lochore, Fife, Scotland":"Lochore, Fife, Scotland","Scotland":"Scotland","Fife, Scotland":"Fife, Scotland","Lochore, Fife, Scotland, United Kingdom":"Lochore, Fife, Skotlanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1210–1290":"1210–1290","1210–Female":"1210–Décédée","1240–1325":"1240–1325","1196–1290":"1196–1290","1196–1235":"1196–1235","1325":"1325","1235":"1235","1210":"1210","before 1210":"avant 1210","about 1235":"environ 1235","1240":"1240","1196":"1196","1290":"1290","Lochore, Fife, Scotland":"Lochore, Fife, Écosse","Scotland":"Écosse","Fife, Scotland":"Fife, Écosse","Lochore, Fife, Scotland, United Kingdom":"Lochore, Fife, Écosse, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Lorsque Sir David Lochore est né en 1210, à Lochore, Fife, Écosse, son père, Sir Duncan Lochore, avait 14 ans et sa mère, Mrs Lochore, avait 15 ans. Il a eu au m